<br>
Being unable to remove various items from the screens is really odd.  For some reason you can't just delete them, it results in an error.  For example, I tried to delete the invite and disband buttons from the group window since I am used to using ctrl-i and ctrl-d.  For some reason VI has it set to look for thee and crash if not there.<br>
<br>
In any case, the way to do it is like you did, position it out of the window or else chance the size of the item to 0,0.  I like the resizing it to zero tall and wide myself.<br>
<br>
Tgt % is eqtype 29.  Yes, use the label for it.  Also, remember you need to add a text label that has &quot;%&quot; idf you want it.  The eqtype is just the number.<br>
